<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8308583>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Species of Boosia Speta. 1. Boosia macrocentra (Baker) Speta from Phillips (1924: pl. 142, as Urginea macrocentra Baker); 2. Boosia flagellaris (T.J.Edwards et al.) Mart.-Azorín et al. from Edwards et al. (2005: 123, as Drimia flagellaris Edwards et al.)." ;
